snippet.title: [Level 1 Stats] Valkyria Chronicles 3 E2 - Extra Missions: The Targeted Stockpile Goods - 3 Turns
snippet.description:
Mission Name: The Targeted Stockpile Goods
Mission Objectives: Defend supply crate for 8 turns OR all enemy units defeated
Restrictions: Kurt and Riela must deploy
Grade: ★★★★★
Ace Name: Tokuna the Restless
Ace Drop 1: Grendel
Ace Drop 2: None
Ranking: S: 6 | A: 7 | B: 8

This is a DLC mission that is not included in the "E2" version of Valkyria Chronicles 3 and therefore, entirely in Japanese. Translations may not be 100% accurate but it is at least something to go off.
